cast.overview: When danger threatens her camp, the fierce and highly skilled Comanche warrior Naru sets out to protect her people. But the prey she stalks turns out to be a highly evolved alien predator with a technically advanced arsenal.
cast.title: Prey

details.biography: Stormee Kipp, who is Blackfeet, is the son of Michelle Kipp and the late Gerad Kipp. He is the grandson of Dr. LaNada Warjack, Gigi Kipp, and Loretta Evening. He is 20 years old and is currently attending the University of Montana where he is majoring in psychology.
details.name: Stormee Kipp
